# GitHub OAuth Configuration
# ============================
# To set up GitHub OAuth for this admin dashboard:
#
# 1. Go to https://github.com/settings/developers
# 2. Click "New OAuth App"
# 3. Fill in:
#    - Application name: Aashma Bidari Admin
#    - Homepage URL: https://aashmabidari.com.np
#    - Authorization callback URL: https://aashmabidari.com.np/admin/github-callback.html
# 4. Copy the Client ID and update it in:
#    - login.html (GITHUB_CLIENT_ID variable)
#    - admin/admin.js (GITHUB_CLIENT_ID constant)
#
# 5. For the token exchange (OAuth requires server-side secret), deploy a
#    Cloudflare Worker or Vercel Edge Function with the Client Secret.
#    Example worker code is in admin/github-oauth-worker.js
#
# NO TOKENS NEED TO BE STORED HERE - OAuth handles it automatically!

GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=Ov23liZAE6fT8eATFv2P
GITHUB_OAUTH_CALLBACK=https://aashmabidari.com.np/admin/github-callback.html
GITHUB_REPO=aashmabidari.com.np
GITHUB_BRANCH=main
